latestPosts.caption:
Words fall short to describe the feeling of taking a holy dip at the Triveni Sangam Mahakumbh 2025 🕉️

Monday, 10/2/2025 ✨ What an extraordinary day! What a divine feeling 🤍 Once in a 144 year opportunity!

Blessed to be born in the century, where we could experience something this powerful. So grateful to be part of this incredible journey, surrounded by the beauty of our culture and spirituality. This snan has left me feeling rejuvenated, humbled, and more connected to my roots than ever before….. har har gange! Om namah shivay. Hare krishna!

The whole way to Prayag raj was impossible without my dearest friend hema @blossam_2309 and this super hero commando Atul pandey 🙏🏼

Experiencing the unforgettable road trip through the new #delhimumbaiexpressway was an ultimate bliss 🧿😍
